{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1615,"text":"So I grew up in East Los Angeles,"},{"time":4115,"text":"not even realizing I was poor."},{"time":6286,"text":"My dad was a high-ranking gang member who ran the streets."},{"time":10403,"text":"Everyone knew who I was,"},{"time":11702,"text":"so I thought I was a pretty big deal, and I was protected,"},{"time":15152,"text":"and even though my dad spent most of my life"},{"time":17721,"text":"in and out of jail,"},{"time":19070,"text":"I had an amazing mom who was just fiercely independent."},{"time":23571,"text":"She worked at the local high school"},{"time":25080,"text":"as a secretary in the dean's office,"},{"time":27635,"text":"so she got to see all the kids that got thrown out of class,"},{"time":30325,"text":"for whatever reason, who were waiting to be disciplined."},{"time":33163,"text":"Man, her office was packed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36954,"text":"So, see, kids like us, we have a lot of things to deal with"},{"time":40751,"text":"outside of school,"},{"time":42309,"text":"and sometimes we're just not ready to focus."},{"time":45226,"text":"But that doesn't mean that we can't."},{"time":47556,"text":"It just takes a little bit more."},{"time":49743,"text":"Like, I remember one day I found my dad"},{"time":52848,"text":"convulsing, foaming at the mouth,"},{"time":55192,"text":"OD-ing on the bathroom floor."},{"time":57406,"text":"Really, do you think that doing my homework that night"},{"time":59879,"text":"was at the top of my priority list?"},{"time":62391,"text":"Not so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63858,"text":"But I really needed a support network,"},{"time":66991,"text":"a group of people who were going to help me"},{"time":69316,"text":"make sure that I wasn't going to be"},{"time":71536,"text":"a victim of my own circumstance,"},{"time":74191,"text":"that they were going to push me"},{"time":75805,"text":"beyond what I even thought I could do."},{"time":78370,"text":"I needed teachers, in the classroom, every day,"},{"time":81839,"text":"who were going to say, \"You can move beyond that.\""},{"time":85584,"text":"And unfortunately, the local junior high"},{"time":88862,"text":"was not going to offer that."},{"time":90971,"text":"It was gang-infested, huge teacher turnover rate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94805,"text":"So my mom said, \"You're going on a bus"},{"time":97978,"text":"an hour and a half away from where we live every day.\""},{"time":103191,"text":"So for the next two years, that's what I did."},{"time":105553,"text":"I took a school bus to the fancy side of town."},{"time":110040,"text":"And eventually, I ended up at a school"},{"time":112965,"text":"where there was a mixture."},{"time":114529,"text":"There were some people who were really gang-affiliated,"},{"time":117207,"text":"and then there were those of us"},{"time":118672,"text":"really trying to make it to high school."},{"time":120666,"text":"Well, trying to stay out of trouble was a little unavoidable."},{"time":124169,"text":"You had to survive."},{"time":125883,"text":"You just had to do things sometimes."},{"time":128536,"text":"So there were a lot of teachers who were like,"},{"time":130889,"text":"\"She's never going to make it."},{"time":132315,"text":"She has an issue with authority."},{"time":133906,"text":"She's not going to go anywhere.\""},{"time":135549,"text":"Some teachers completely wrote me off as a lost cause."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139642,"text":"But then, they were very surprised"},{"time":142809,"text":"when I graduated from high school."},{"time":146000,"text":"I was accepted to Pepperdine University,"},{"time":148862,"text":"and I came back to the same school that I attended"},{"time":151985,"text":"to be a special ed assistant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153896,"text":"And then I told them, \"I want to be a teacher.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":158449,"text":"And boy, they were like, \"What? Why?"},{"time":161673,"text":"Why would you want to do that?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":163193,"text":"So I began my teaching career"},{"time":165479,"text":"at the exact same middle school that I attended,"},{"time":169007,"text":"and I really wanted to try to save more kids"},{"time":172438,"text":"who were just like me."},{"time":174515,"text":"And so every year, I share my background with my kids,"},{"time":177715,"text":"because they need to know that everyone has a story,"},{"time":180772,"text":"everyone has a struggle,"},{"time":183139,"text":"and everyone needs help along the way."},{"time":186893,"text":"And I am going to be their help along the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191021,"text":"So as a rookie teacher, I created opportunity."},{"time":197089,"text":"I had a kid one day come into my class"},{"time":199735,"text":"having been stabbed the night before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202943,"text":"I was like, \"You need to go to a hospital,"},{"time":205439,"text":"the school nurse, something.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":208714,"text":"He's like, \"No, Miss, I'm not going."},{"time":210875,"text":"I need to be in class because I need to graduate.\""},{"time":213643,"text":"So he knew that I was not going to let him be a victim"},{"time":217035,"text":"of his circumstance,"},{"time":218812,"text":"but we were going to push forward and keep moving on."},{"time":222850,"text":"And this idea of creating a safe haven for our kids"},{"time":226740,"text":"and getting to know exactly what they're going through,"},{"time":230856,"text":"getting to know their families -- I wanted that,"},{"time":234112,"text":"but I couldn't do it in a school with 1,600 kids,"},{"time":239592,"text":"and teachers turning over year after year after year."},{"time":243066,"text":"How do you get to build those relationships?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":247118,"text":"So we created a new school."},{"time":250705,"text":"And we created"},{"time":252184,"text":"the San Fernando Institute for Applied Media."},{"time":255722,"text":"And we made sure that we were still attached"},{"time":259194,"text":"to our school district for funding, for support."},{"time":263232,"text":"But with that, we were going to gain freedom:"},{"time":266349,"text":"freedom to hire the teachers"},{"time":268602,"text":"that we knew were going to be effective;"},{"time":271924,"text":"freedom to control the curriculum"},{"time":274664,"text":"so that we're not doing lesson 1.2 on page five, no;"},{"time":280302,"text":"and freedom to control a budget,"},{"time":283022,"text":"to spend money where it matters,"},{"time":285606,"text":"not how a district or a state says you have to do it."},{"time":289847,"text":"We wanted those freedoms."},{"time":292150,"text":"But now, shifting an entire paradigm,"},{"time":294726,"text":"it hasn't been an easy journey, nor is it even complete."},{"time":298871,"text":"But we had to do it."},{"time":301221,"text":"Our community deserved a new way of doing things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305342,"text":"And as the very first pilot middle school"},{"time":308868,"text":"in all of Los Angeles Unified School District,"},{"time":312093,"text":"you better believe there was some opposition."},{"time":315069,"text":"And it was out of fear --"},{"time":317192,"text":"fear of, well, what if they get it wrong?"},{"time":320415,"text":"Yeah, what if we get it wrong?"},{"time":322600,"text":"But what if we get it right?"},{"time":324854,"text":"And we did."},{"time":326929,"text":"So even though teachers were against it"},{"time":329540,"text":"because we employ one-year contracts --"},{"time":332121,"text":"you can't teach, or you don't want to teach,"},{"time":336190,"text":"you don't get to be at my school with my kids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339250,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":346014,"text":"So in our third year, how did we do it?"},{"time":349686,"text":"Well, we're making school worth coming to every day."},{"time":353117,"text":"We make our kids feel like they matter to us."},{"time":355878,"text":"We make our curriculum rigorous and relevant to them,"},{"time":359766,"text":"and they use all the technology that they're used to."},{"time":362351,"text":"Laptops, computers, tablets -- you name it, they have it."},{"time":365278,"text":"Animation, software, moviemaking software, they have it all."},{"time":369196,"text":"And because we connect it to what they're doing â€”"},{"time":373009,"text":"For example, they made public service announcements"},{"time":376211,"text":"for the Cancer Society."},{"time":377837,"text":"These were played in the local trolley system."},{"time":380661,"text":"Teaching elements of persuasion,"},{"time":382668,"text":"it doesn't get any more real than that."},{"time":385588,"text":"Our state test scores have gone up"},{"time":387749,"text":"more than 80 points since we've become our own school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390738,"text":"But it's taken all stakeholders, working together --"},{"time":393833,"text":"teachers and principals on one-year contracts,"},{"time":397017,"text":"working over and above and beyond their contract hours"},{"time":400841,"text":"without compensation."},{"time":403877,"text":"And it takes a school board member"},{"time":406096,"text":"who is going to lobby for you and say,"},{"time":408048,"text":"\"Know, the district is trying to impose this,"},{"time":410476,"text":"but you have the freedom to do otherwise.\""},{"time":413509,"text":"And it takes an active parent center"},{"time":416073,"text":"who is not only there, showing a presence every day,"},{"time":420153,"text":"but who is part of our governance,"},{"time":423020,"text":"making decisions for their kids, our kids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":428024,"text":"Because why should our students have to go"},{"time":430629,"text":"so far away from where they live?"},{"time":433608,"text":"They deserve a quality school in their neighborhood,"},{"time":437332,"text":"a school that they can be proud to say they attend,"},{"time":440505,"text":"and a school that the community can be proud of as well,"},{"time":444173,"text":"and they need teachers to fight for them every day"},{"time":448371,"text":"and empower them to move beyond their circumstances."},{"time":453704,"text":"Because it's time that kids like me"},{"time":456420,"text":"stop being the exception, and we become the norm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461142,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":462451,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}